--- orig_t041_2/ForgeRoot/.forge/policies/security-gates.forge	1970-01-01 00:00:00.000000000 +0000
+++ work_t041/ForgeRoot/.forge/policies/security-gates.forge	2026-04-19 09:41:30.275523298 +0000
